        <![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1NBZIgjO0U"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/T1NBZIgjO0U/maxresdefault.jpg" /></a></p><br /><p style="clear: both"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1NBZIgjO0U"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/T1NBZIgjO0U/0.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1NBZIgjO0U"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/T1NBZIgjO0U/1.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1NBZIgjO0U"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/T1NBZIgjO0U/2.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1NBZIgjO0U"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/T1NBZIgjO0U/3.jpg" /></a></p>
<hr style="clear:both" />

<p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><strong># -00:51 為什麼常見的影片總結 AI 不一定能做出總結？</strong></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">不是啦。這些YouTube的總結工具。先別急著罵。你有看到上面寫著。常見的YouTube總結AI。都是靠影片的字幕做分析。但如果影片沒有CC字幕。那這些AI就。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">比如這支16年前的Bass教學。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">聰明的Max AI。就用下方的網友留下的。5000多則留言。總結出影片在說什麽。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">而且最需要影片總結的。不就是那些沒字幕。又看不完的超長直播影片嗎。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_51.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=51" target="_blank"><strong># -01:18 【重要】泛科學院隔週四中午有直播！</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">像是泛科學院。每隔周四中午12點半的直播。含金量極高。講的都是最新AI新聞。但你可能非常忙。一秒鐘幾十萬上下。連一個小時都抽不出來看重播。這時候就非常需要。影片總結服務。這些沒字幕的影片該怎麽辦呢。現在AI辨識語音也很厲害啦。就先語音辨識。再把這些辨識結果。交給ChatGPT之類的AI。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_78.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=78" target="_blank"><strong># -01:30 用 AI 語音轉文字，幫助影片總結 AI</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">做逐字稿分析不就好了嗎。接下來我想要分享兩個。我覺得好用。而且免費的語音轉文字AI。Whisper JAX 跟 Memo AI。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_90.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=90" target="_blank"><strong># -02:33 Whisper JAX 操作介紹</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">先來說說Whisper JAX。你可以直接Google搜尋就能夠找到。不用註冊也不用費用。點進去就可以直接使用。如果你懶到連搜尋都不想按。可以在下方資訊欄。找到Whisper JAX的連結。語音轉文字的AI有很多。像之前介紹的Vocol AI就是。Whisper JAX 除了免費。且逐字稿品質不差之外呢。更重要的是。Whisper JAX. 只要輸入YouTube影片連結。就能完成逐字稿啦。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">首先點選上面的YouTube。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">在這邊輸入YouTube影片的連結。下面選擇Transcribe。按下送出鍵。哎唷 全部擠在一起。是要怎麽看啦。啊別急著罵。這是錯誤示範。提醒大家在送出之前。要把下面這個。Return timestamps 勾起來。才會跑出有時間序的分段內容。Whisper JAX 雖然有翻譯。Translate的功能。但只能翻譯成英文。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">不過問題不大。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">只要有了逐字稿。一切都好辦。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_152.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">覺得Whisper JAX。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_153.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=153" target="_blank"><strong># -03:14 Memo AI 安裝、註冊介紹</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">還要把逐字稿貼到其他地方分析。很麻煩嗎。或者是看英文影片。需要品質好的翻譯字幕嗎。別擔心。我跟你有一樣的想法。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接下來介紹的Memo AI。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">不只有Whisper JAX的所有功能。還可以串其他語言模型。讓你三個願望一次滿足。首先到官網下載Memo AI。安裝完成之後。打開Memo AI。會看到鍵入金鑰的畫面。這個時候你要到官網註冊。在這邊填Email送出。然後到你註冊的信箱收信。就可以看到Memo AI寄的金鑰給你。複製金鑰。輸入Memo AI就可以使用啦。進入Memo AI 能看到。上面有輸入YouTube連結的地方。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_194.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=194" target="_blank"><strong># -04:24 Memo AI 操作介紹</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">輸入之後點選轉譯。就會看到設定畫面。這邊可以選擇原本檔案的語言。就可以直接用自動偵測就好。品質的部分。免費版只能用極速跟均衡。只有購買Pro版的才能使用高質量。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">不過對一般人來說。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">均衡就已經很夠用了。而且Memo AI的模型。是在本機電腦上運作。如果你的電腦不夠好。也會跑不出來。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後選擇是否用GPU加速。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">有的話可以選一下。好啦 現在按下轉寫。就會開始制作影片逐字稿了。完成逐字稿之後呢。你可以在右上方選擇翻譯。這樣就會把整份逐字稿。翻成你想要的語言了。翻譯的方式有免費的Google翻譯。你也可以自己串API。用ChatGPT來做翻譯。而在主畫面的下方。你會看到總結的按鈕。點下去就會要你設定API。這個時候你只要登入Open AI的官網。取得API KEY 之後。複製到翻譯設置中的Open AI。左邊是輸入API KEY 的欄位。右邊是輸入代理伺服器的位置。一般來說留空白就可以了。先按下總結鍵。影片總結就完成啦。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_264.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=264" target="_blank"><strong># -04:54 Memo AI 支援心智圖與雙語字幕</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">Memo AI結合了ChatGPT之後。除了可以將影片內容做總結。它還能夠生成AI心智圖。看起來非常厲害對吧。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">好啦 這其實就是有結構的列點整理。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">對我來說。這可是比摘要還要容易閱讀呢。另外Memo還可以將字幕匯出。直接把英文字幕。跟翻譯好的中文字幕同步顯示。這樣子看YouTube還可以學外語。把滑手機看影片。一秒就變成富有教育意義的活動。現在我們可以抬頭挺胸。看YouTube影片了。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/T1NBZIgjO0U_294.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/T1NBZIgjO0U&t=294" target="_blank"><strong># -05:17 總結</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">既然Memo AI這麽好用。誰還需要Whisper JAX 呢。誰想得到A編居然還在用。10年前的筆電。根本跑不動Memo AI呢。而Whisper JAX 就成為他唯一的選擇。如果這支影片對你有幫助的話。請幫我在影片下方點個喜歡。並且把這支影片分享給需要的朋友。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後別忘了訂閱泛科學院的頻道。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">我們下支影片再見囉 掰掰。</p>

<hr style="clear:both" />
